  <description><![CDATA[<p>Situated in the heart of the Savoie area of the French Alps is the attractive village of Belle Plagne and the Chalet Hotel des Deux Domaines. The village is made up of a cluster of stone and wood buildings and a pedestrianised village centre, all decked with flowers. There are numerous paths radiating outwards towards pine forests and open meadows and superb views are guaranteed. Included in a week’s stay are two wanderwalks, a trip to Annecy, a river rafting excursion and a host of hotel activities including wine tasting, a talk on the local area, bridge evening, a quiz and a cookery demonstration.</p>]]></description>
