  <excursions><![CDATA[<p><strong>Included Free Excursion </strong></p>
<p><strong>Annecy Friday, full day</strong><br />Visit beautiful Annecy with its old town dominated by canals and historic buildings. The market is open in the morning, then stroll in the lakeside gardens or take a cruise on the clear blue lake.</p>
<p><strong>Book Locally <br /></strong></p>
<p><strong>White Water Rafting £63</strong></p>
<p>Negotiate the rapids of the River Isère with a professional guide in<br />groups of eight. A real exciting team experience. Includes return travel to<br />the river. (For 11 yrs and above).</p>
<p><strong>Canyoning £52</strong></p>
<p>An adventurous day out, sliding jumping and climbing through waterfalls and gorges carved out by the river. Run by a professional guide.</p>
<p><strong>Paragliding £52</strong></p>
<p>Take an unforgettable and breathtaking flight over the beautiful scenery<br />of La Plagne.</p>
<p><em>Prices are shown for guidance only</em></p>]]></excursions>
