<h2>Improve/Learn Bridge</h2>
<p>Enjoy instruction from our resident experts in the tactics of Bridge. Perfect for beginners and for those looking to improve their card skills. We offer sessions on four days of instruction and play, culminating in a match on the fifth evening. Sessions take place at varying times during the week and don't forget Mini Bridge is also available for our 7+ players. Our leaders are qualified English Bridge Union instructors with plenty of experience and enthusiasm.<br /><strong>When: </strong>14 nights of instruction from 23 July until 5 August<br /><strong>Where:</strong> Chalet Hotel Des Deux Domaines,<strong><br />Duration:</strong> 4 sessions of 2 hours<br /><strong>Min/max numbers:</strong> 15-25<br /><strong>Price:</strong> FREE</p>]]></experienceMore>
